item.title: Lunar Lander using DQN
item.description: OpenAI Gym provides the LunarLander-v2 environment which challenges users to train the lander agent to successfully solve the environment. The environment is considered solved when it achieves 200 reward points. This is typically achieved by successfully landing the agent on the landing pads.
